  "texts": [
    "Analytical AI has shown its value, but generative AI holds even greater potential, offering a wider range of application scenarios.",
    "It has the power not only to elevate existing financial services but also to pioneer new business models.",
    "Looking ahead, U.S. financial institutions should be proactive in exploring the applications of generative AI within the finance sector.",
    "Moreover, while ensuring security and compliance, these institutions could benefit from partnerships with tech companies.",
    "Leveraging their respective strengths, they can accelerate the deep integration of AI technology and financial services, thereby boosting the international competitiveness of the United States' financial technology sector.The second is to attach equal importance to supervision and development, and consider the development of AI financial regulation in advance."
